# Insecticides Product Images

Place insecticide product images in this folder. Images are loaded automatically based on product names in the products database.

## Expected Images

- cypertox-25.jpg
- projector-320.jpg
- almite-2-0.jpg
- metholing-90.jpg
- carnon-700.jpg
- alphameo-10.jpg
- antibug-224.jpg
- cabino-150.jpg
- emazote-5.jpg
- sensor-240.jpg

Each image filename should match the `imageUrl` property in the products database (without the folder path).
